title: 12/28/21 DPS Hour 3   Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 12/28/21 DPS Hour 3   Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
description:
The Lakers have lost five games in a row. There is plenty of blame to go around, but Rob puts much of it on Russell Westbrook and Lebron's decision to bring Westbrook into the fold. TJ thinks all will be fine with the team once they get their team healthy and on track. Tom Brady has thrown one touchdown pass total in the last two games. Rob thinks Brady is overhyped as an MVP candidate and should be left out of that discussion.
